            <div class=3D"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summ=
ary field--label-hidden field--item"><div id=3D"savings-calculator">
<div class=3D"intro">
<p>Smoking cigarettes is expensive. Use our calculator to find out how much=
 of your money is going up in smoke. For reference, the average price of a =
pack of cigarettes is $8.39 in the United States.</p>
</div>

<div class=3D"card card-gray col-lg-12">
<div class=3D"row">
<div class=3D"col-md-6">
<form class=3D"calculator">
<div class=3D"form-group"><label>How many cigarettes do you smoke per day?<=
span class=3D"red">*</span></label> <input aria-label=3D"" class=3D"form-co=
ntrol cigarette-number" max=3D"100" min=3D"1" placeholder=3D"Enter number o=
f cigarettes" type=3D"number"></div>
<!-- /.form-group -->

<div class=3D"form-group"><label>How much do you pay per pack?</label>

<div class=3D"input-group"><span class=3D"input-group-addon">$</span> <inpu=
t aria-label=3D"" class=3D"form-control cigarette-cost" max=3D"100" min=3D"=
1" placeholder=3D"0.00" type=3D"number"></div>
<!-- /.input-group --></div>
<!-- /.form-group -->

<div class=3D"spacer-20">&nbsp;</div>

<p class=3D"small"><span class=3D"red">*</span> Required Fields</p>
<button class=3D"btn btn-default">CALCULATE</button></form>
</div>
<!-- /.col-md-6 -->

<div class=3D"col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
<h3 class=3D"first">Results</h3>

<div class=3D"table-responsive">
<table class=3D"table table-bordered table-striped savings-calculator">
	<thead>
		<tr>
